            ResourceGroupName = "search-service",

)

func main() {

		example, err := apimanagement.LookupApi(ctx, &apimanagement.LookupApiArgs{
			Name:              "search-api",
			ApiManagementName: "search-api-management",
			ResourceGroupName: "search-service",
			Revision:          "2",
		}, nil)
		if err != nil {

		}

		return nil
	})
}
